{"tid":1596044,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[本地文宣] 宣揚黑警暴行 解！散！警！隊！","createTime":"2019-09-26T10:41:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T03:50:25.000Z","uid":191723,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5d42c1227b5e355f2b9ee3057866a717e9f811c6","tid":1596044,"uid":191723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T10:41:30.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今次文宣重點係宣揚黑警暴力行為、黑警濫用警權、選擇性執法、圍毆打市民。<br />\n要求成立獨立調查委員會，否則解散警隊！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n世界已然步入資訊年代，本團隊利用網絡資訊的高度流通性特點，可以更快將消息、黑警暴行散播出去。網絡文宣亦都唔怕會被藍絲廢老、撕紙狗清除相關宣傳資訊，達至更高效率以及宣傳效果更佳的文宣方法。<br />\n<br />\n如果你支持網絡文宣請幫推上熱門及捐款。團隊會趕在9月30日前推出廣告，全民黑衣v煞迎國慶！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">宣傳目標對象</span></ins></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">直至今時今日仍然盲目的中立派</span></span></strong></ins><br />\n中立派絕對係最容易拉攏嘅對象，佢地係最容易受到動搖，藉著網絡文宣不斷播出黑警暴行、警黑合作、林奠漠視民意等內容、希望可以喚醒佢地嘅良知。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: teal;\">淺藍絲</span></ins></strong><br />\n淺藍絲都係文宣主要對象之一，亦都係比較容易拉攏嘅目標。有巴打成功說服自己嘅藍絲父母支持抗爭運動，愈多人支持呢場運動勝利嘅機會就愈大，因此任何一個可以拉攏目標嘅機會都唔可以放過。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: navy;\">藍絲</span></ins></strong><br />\n藍絲係無腦，是非黑白都分唔清楚，只係睇cctvb剪頭剪尾嘅垃圾片段就判斷義士破壞社會安寧搞搞震，因此希望佢地睇完文宣嘅內容會了解到黑警所作所為，從而改變立場反對黑警。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">廣告宣傳內容</span></span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n廣告內容重中之重是宣揚黑警暴行。黑警以謊言掩飾暴行，再將責任推向義士。<br />\n黑警選擇性執法，對義士就暴力鎮壓，對藍絲的施襲者卻加以保護、不斷縱容及高調放生。美其名維持社會安寧，實則是濫用過份暴力協助維穩政權，目的達致民眾禁聲的效果。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q4JMUaR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq4JMUaR.jpg&h=21b0467b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">廣告宣傳平台</span></span></strong></ins><br />\n<br />\nGoogle 廣告 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q6wOn2N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq6wOn2N.png&h=1e43551d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nYoutube 廣告 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/giaSPKK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgiaSPKK.jpg&h=f6471fec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nFacebook 廣告 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3pGVNws.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3pGVNws.png&h=a7fee749&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n宣傳對象年齡將會設定為40至65+，我相信大部份年青人都係支持反送中，藍絲嘅年青人亦好難說服佢地，因此為了節省點撃費用，故不會將年齡設定為年青人範圍，亦希望黃絲們見到廣告都唔好手多去點撃，因為每一次點撃都要畀錢。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">Google 廣告</span></ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n廣告類型:圖像廣告<br />\n暫定三種廣告類型<br />\n300X250 圖像廣告<br />\n250X250 圖像廣告<br />\n320X50  圖像廣告<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">預計Google Ads費用</span><br />\n點撃費用：HK$2.50<br />\n展示次數：2,000,000<br />\n點擊數 : 2%展示次數<br />\n總成本 : HK$100,000<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">Youtube 廣告</span></span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n廣告類型：影片<br />\n暫定兩種廣告類型<br />\n15秒廣告 (可略過式插播)<br />\n5秒廣告 (不可略過式插播)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">預計Youtube費用（Google Ads「影片廣告系列」）</span><br />\n將會總廣告預算為HK$50000<br />\n*根據眾籌所得金額會有所調整<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Facebook 廣告</span></span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n廣告類型：影片<br />\n廣告格式為單一圖像或影片<br />\n影片長度：15秒<br />\n長寬比：直向（4:5）<br />\n影片格式：.mp4<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">預計Facebook廣告費用</span><br />\n將會設定總廣告預算為HK$50000<br />\n*根據眾籌所得金額會有所調整<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>其他</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n三個平台廣告預定推出日期為9月30日，趕在10月1日前推出，預定廣告持續時間為1個月 <br />\n<br />\n三個平台廣告都會根據眾籌金額而調整廣告預算，務求讓更多中立派、藍絲可以清楚了解黑警暴行，從而改變立場。<br />\n<br />\n所有眾籌資金將用作文宣廣告費用，本團隊絕不會私取任何金錢，全部廣告費用都會清楚在Telegram channel和眾籌頁面公佈，每星期更新一次廣告費用支出，因此大家都能夠清楚了解所有費用去向。<br />\n歡迎大家追蹤tg channel，所有有關反送中運動的資訊和廣告費用都會在此tg channel公佈，有問題想了解亦可以tg我。<br />\n<br />\n眾籌連結： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2li20IJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2li20IJ&d=0M2zeZ419d%2BEsiU1FPoAwwKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=e0e56504\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2li20IJ</a><br />\nTelegram channel：<a href=\"https://t.me/AntiELABHongKong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FAntiELABHongKong&d=0M2zeZ419d%2BEsiU1FPoAwwKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=a47b3613\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/AntiELABHongKong</a><br />\nTelegram：<a href=\"https://t.me/Anti_ELAB_HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FAnti_ELAB_HK&d=0M2zeZ419d%2BEsiU1FPoAwwKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=bdb5b47c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Anti_ELAB_HK</a>"},{"pid":"5bb5f0c74e40ade6491abc3cc2a38ca800b375a6","tid":1596044,"uid":191723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T10:41:41.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"306467c52f1a4a44ac165bf5e03ab01b323c48d4","tid":1596044,"uid":191723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T10:41:51.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"e64387a3e40f7fd926561d43fe18051c249e1332","tid":1596044,"uid":191723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T10:42:01.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"8a8878f384983fc33d320c99fd268261e5107054","tid":1596044,"uid":191723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T10:42:11.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"4c3591ac7a87fc20d575c138504ecf7e9b281602","tid":1596044,"uid":191723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T10:42:21.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"6c05c18a80719b19dc2179c416df1cf6c248b5bb","tid":1596044,"uid":191723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T10:42:34.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"653127c930113534fdbf65228c08b90b8652d96d","tid":1596044,"uid":191723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi